author: scottbw
msg: Added deprecation notices for legacy API methods for widgets that have been superseded by the W3C and Wave Gadget specs (e.g. widget.sharedDataForKey, widget.preferenceForKey) and extended the syntax analyzer to generate warnings both for these and for any calls to the (undocumented) Wookie-specific extensions such as widget.show, widget.lock.
